body_html: Find a better way instead of removing the old version: I am using Ubuntu and that version comes from Ubuntu package python-protobuf. I uninstalled tensorflow and the new protobuf (sudo pip uninstall protobuf) and then upgrade the existing one using "sudo pip install --upgrade protobuf".
